---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy"
	description="Privacy policy and data handling practices for Drifting Miles"
	pubDate={new Date('January 1 2024')}
>
	<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
	<p>At Drifting Miles, we take your privacy seriously. This policy outlines how we handle your information.</p>

	<h3>Information Collection</h3>
	<p>We collect minimal information necessary to provide you with the best possible experience:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Basic analytics data to improve our content</li>
		<li>Email addresses if you choose to subscribe to our newsletter</li>
		<li>Comments and interactions if you engage with our content</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Data Usage</h3>
	<p>Your information is used solely for:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Improving our travel content and recommendations</li>
		<li>Sending relevant travel updates and newsletters (if subscribed)</li>
		<li>Responding to your queries and comments</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Data Protection</h3>
	<p>We implement security measures to protect your data and never share personal information with third parties without consent.</p>

	<h3>Contact</h3>
	<p>For privacy-related questions, please contact us through our contact form.</p>
</Layout>